<title>USA: Stolt Comex files for share offering.</title>
<headline>Stolt Comex files for share offering.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-02-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Stolt Comex Seaway SA said on Tuesday it filed for a public offering of 3.5 million common shares.</p>
<p>Concurrent with the completion of the offering, Stolt-Nielsen SA will convert part of the intercompany debt owed to it into equity by acquiring six million Stolt Comex Seaway Class B shares, the company said.</p>
<p>The 6.5 million class B shares is equivalent to three million common shares, the company said. The offering will be underwritten by Schroder Wertheim, Furman Selz, Howard Weil, Labouisse, Friedrichs and Simmons &amp; Co International.</p>
